    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal;" translate="true">User can import from a defined SCD/CID/ICD file or load from a saved file to quickly start the configurations.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal;" translate="true">The &quot;Scout&quot; button provide an online GOOSE event detection.</text></para>
